n.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%E1%BA%ADt/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Mai-hoa/poem-r0X22jqT9P_WO2h0MRIHOA">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Mai hoa” - 奉和御製梅花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Quang-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-uKsiCb0CAnZcZT9U9On7LQ">Nguyễn Quang Bật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Mai-hoa/poem-0rLHfPBUbVnuTd7Ynjxraw">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Mai hoa” - 奉和御製梅花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/author-7XXX3GnZ0T6el9FCsBAeug">Ngô Hoán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%E1%BA%A5t-tam-tam/poem-W0DoimPowPLoE-4Hcdu-hw">Thất tam tam - 失三三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-dlHnmd0KjGsb0OLTGFEOjQ">Tống Lưu hiệu thư tòng quân - 送劉校書從軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/author-UC91PIpcFalgwS4PbK2Lpg">Dương Quýnh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
